{"build_type":"library","module_name":"first-fit-pop-arena-chunk","package_name":"first-fit-pop-arena-chunk","description":"Recursive FIRST-FIT pop from this thread's g_arena_free_list: walk (prev,cur) until a chunk whose header size (slot0) >= want, unlink it (fix prev->next or the g_arena_free_list head), return it; return 0 if none fits. Enables one mixed-size thread-local economy (2 GiB blocks + 1 MiB stack/region chunks on one list) — head-only fit would strand the big block behind small ones. Single-threaded (owning thread only), no atomics.","function_definitions":{"first-fit-pop-arena-chunk":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"prev","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"cur","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"want","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"one","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":1},{"instruction_type":"conditional_branch","condition_type":"numeric_compare","operator":"==","lhs":{"value":"cur"},"rhs":{"value":"zero"},"branch_on_success":[{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"zero"}}],"branch_on_failure":[]},{"instruction_type":"array_read","dest":"csize","base":"cur","index":"zero","scale":8},{"instruction_type":"conditional_branch","condition_type":"numeric_compare","operator":">=","lhs":{"value":"csize"},"rhs":{"value":"want"},"branch_on_success":[{"instruction_type":"array_read","dest":"link","base":"cur","index":"one","scale":8},{"instruction_type":"conditional_branch","condition_type":"numeric_compare","operator":"==","lhs":{"value":"prev"},"rhs":{"value":"zero"},"branch_on_success":[{"instruction_type":"global_write","name":"g_arena_free_list","value":"link"}],"branch_on_failure":[{"instruction_type":"array_write","base":"prev","index":"one","value":"link","scale":8}]},{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"cur"}}],"branch_on_failure":[]},{"instruction_type":"array_read","dest":"nxt","base":"cur","index":"one","scale":8},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"first-fit-pop-arena-chunk","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"cur"},{"kind":"var","value":"nxt"},{"kind":"var","value":"want"}],"result_assignment_variable":"r","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"r"}}]}}}